properties.headline: Dense Fog Advisory issued February 11 at 12:08PM CST until February 12 at 12:00PM CST by NWS New Orleans LA
properties.description:
* WHAT...Dense fog will reduce visibility to 1/4 to 1/2 NM.

* WHERE...Lake Pontchartrain and Lake Maurepas.

* WHEN...From 6 PM this evening to noon CST Wednesday.

* ADDITIONAL DETAILS... The Dense Fog Advisory that was in effect
for the rest of the afternoon has been canceled based out of
latest area webcams and observations, however will go in effect
again at 6PM CST this evening.
properties.instruction:
If you must navigate, proceed with caution. Use proper fog
signals. Make sure all running lights are on. Remember to use
your radar and compass.

NWSheadline: DENSE FOG ADVISORY IN EFFECT FROM 6 PM THIS EVENING TO NOON CST WEDNESDAY
